{"tid":1630954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跪求勇武入黎睇下！港島只適宜和理非遊行！","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T18:05:13.000Z","uid":234195,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8bb0b1056ac6fbdb3e0f8e461b834f40b774097c","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大遊行嘅目的唔係為裝修，唔係為打狗，係為表達有幾多人對政府不滿！<br />\n<br />\n如果要裝修可以18區開花，要打狗可以麻包袋。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">當全部人和平遊行，政府用高強度驅散，打壓，更加可以係國際上凸顯港共打壓和平遊行！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n除非想最後一戰，唔係港島真係唔啱勇武！<br />\n<br />\n1.本身地形問題，好容易被截斷人龍再包抄。狗一路向銅鑼灣推進，炮台山又一定重兵，最後一定無路走。<br />\n2.每次都係為對峙而對峙，一定要狗開始衝先走。同狗對峙對佢地消耗極少，反而增加手足被捕機會。睇下今日港島有幾多個警察受傷，又有幾多手足被捕就知。次次係港島都被圍捕，對狗又0損傷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以以後港島大遊行，防暴一驅散就即刻散！造出政府打壓和平遊行嘅景象！</span>"},{"pid":"4f8f8c0902a4284b1404ae4cef4d95fc4c692397","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"f4653f314b4d96364ae1b9ffa7acca6d0cadcb8e","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"fdbad54620b275aef10005bef75a3eebb0002e6c","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ea1b67a0164007dbc92380322b9f1730c5b7b871","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"4c695a1c4ee74bcd125793224a4b528a43263301","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"45c1f516a0122a4ced99d5ec899c9494d1487046","tid":1630954,"uid":150742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\