2019-10-06T14:39:46.000Z","msg":"推啊，次次港島都要圍捕先肯走！ 遊行係只要夠人數就達成目的架啦！對峙只係等被捕！要裝修要打狗快閃係最有效！"},{"pid":"8b4c5e4aa69eebd50489a04dfb6c46fb3d11cd10","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"推啊，次次港島都要圍捕先肯走！ 遊行係只要夠人數就達成目的架啦！對峙只係等被捕！要裝修要打狗快閃係最有效！"},{"pid":"ea29142c10f3dbb6e93fa4813cdeca2eef393fae","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:12.000Z","msg":"一係就唔好再搞遊行，全面轉地下，次次遊行都咁多人被捕"},{"pid":"172aae186d2a02577e55eb177b7192a395590546","tid":1630954,"uid":244636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:45:16.000Z","msg":"同意 和理非行出黎支持勇武所有裝修、神獸行為<br />\n比外媒睇<br />\n唔駛保護我地走 係我地cover，比你地走"},{"pid":"199479a1565db6504d6592ad4adb437e516c606d","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:56:12.000Z","msg":"求推，如果唔同意都一齊諗吓點減少被捕人數"},{"pid":"eb6fa47e26df1eaf238d0dd9d77c9473bd2359ac","tid":1630954,"uid":314350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a93ec28a22cbf8d7039a2ee9c3eeb016910ddf9","tid":1630954,"uid":234195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"350fef3c907b6940a2507f968026915f572ffa20","tid":1630954,"uid":39277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"仲叫人去港島送頭<br />\n<br />\n今日大把得過口罩被拉<br />\n<br />\n講咗港島險地<br />\n<br />\n你為啲所謂畫面致手足於險地<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:35:56.000Z","msg":"今日出咗成日無追新聞，想知有幾多個因為口罩被拉？無可否認，大遊行係製造國際形象最大途徑。如果單論被捕人數，應該轉曬快閃同麻包袋"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:58:05.000Z","msg":"灣仔50個手足俾你地班銅鑼灣人鏈叫停撚累撚死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629982</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hk